text: Kfouri is a surname. It may refer to: *Basil Kfoury (1794-1859), bishop of the Melkite Greek Catholic Archeparchy of Alexandria *Dionysius Kfoury, (1879-1965), bishop of the Melkite Greek Catholic Archeparchy of Alexandria *Wael Kfoury (born awch al Oumara, Zahlé, Lebanon), known by his stage name Wael Kfoury (وائل كفوري), is a Lebanese singer ==See also== *Kafoury
title: Kfoury
